

ServerModManager Control Daemon:

Startup Procedure:
* Check for 7DTD Initialization
  - Set default index.php
  - Update Steam Client
  - Install 7DaysToDie
  - Install SMM Links
  - Set file ownership to allow website to write out to serverconfig.xml, server.expected_status
  - Begin API Loop

Loop API Commands:
<start server>
<stop server>
<force stop server>
<reinstall SMM>
<disable mod>
<disable all mods>
<enable mod>
<enable all mods>
<update mod>
<remove mod>
<add mod>
<update 7dtd>
<backup modpack>
<restore modpack>
<backup server>
<restore server>
